                                    has not yet signed in to TFC.tv Website, a message will appear requesting the Participant
                                    to log in. If the Participant has already signed in to TFC.tv Website, the Participant
                                    will be directed to a page where the Participant can start recording his/her own
                                    lip synch video (the "Video"). </li>
                                <li>5. The Participant will be asked to click the red button at the center of the webpage
